// emotion_sync.hexa — FAA-based emotion-consciousness synchronization
// FAA = ln(right_alpha/F4) - ln(left_alpha/F3)
// FAA > 0: approach/positive, FAA < 0: withdrawal/negative
// 4 phases: baseline, induction, correlation, realtime sync

